<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī dēśē dānya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>taśrīragrahārōtta<unclear>ma</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> śrīmādimayyākhyā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>tatsutassitayaśā gōtrēṇa yaḥ kāśyapaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] nāyakassidimayyēti nāmnā <unclear>viśa</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>dhanavānsatyasaujanyajanmabhūrbhbhūsurōttamaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] mākāṁbāpriyanaṁdanassavilasadveṁgīma<unclear>hī</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vallabha śrīdaṇḍādhipalakṣmarājanikhilakṣmākāryyabhārakṣamaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ācaṁdrārkkamakhaṇḍavarttiru<unclear>cira</unclear>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṁ dīpaṁ śakābdōccayē bhūtēśānanakheṁdugē guṇanidhirbbhīmēśvarāyādiśat <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svasti śakava
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rṣa 1055 ṇṭi śrīmāccālukyavikramasaṁvatsara <unclear>5</unclear>8 gu śrahi <unclear>belva</unclear>lanāṇṭilōna Iṭṭageyagrahā
<lb n="8" break="no"/><unclear>ra</unclear>muna bāgimādimayyanāyakula koḍku gōviṁdarājulayu mākamavva koḍku śrīmallakṣmaṇada
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṇḍanāyakula mahāpradhāni siddimayyanāyakulu śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvaraku dakṣiṇāyana
<lb n="10" break="no"/>saṁkrāṁti nimittamunaṁ beṭṭina yakhaṇḍavartti lōhadaṇḍu diviya 1 ki Ācaṁdrārkkamu neyi sariyiṁcu
<lb n="11" break="no"/><unclear>vāru</unclear>gā bōlu naluvuruṁ būṁṭagā mūṇḍavunaḍapu Eṟiyabhōla bādani yaḍapuna nāvabhōla saṁka
<lb n="12" break="no"/><unclear>ni va</unclear>samunaṁ beṭṭina [InupaE]ḍlu 50 ki nityapaḍi nēti mā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> khitaṁ pedda nācāryyēṇa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
